    <section_number>20</section_number>
    <catch_line>Verification Of Savings Accounts</catch_line>
    <order_by>20</order_by>
    <text>
        At least once in each three year period, every bank shall cause its savings accounts to be verified, to such an extent and in such manner as the commissioner shall require, and under such rules as he may prescribe.
    </text>
